dcterms:description: The ISIC 2018 Task 2 lesion attributes detection dataset contains a total of 2594 samples for training and 1000 images for testing. It includes five types of attributes: Globules, Milia like cyst, Negative network, Pigment network, and Streaks.
dcterms:title: ISIC 2018 Task 2 lesion attributes detection dataset
